Package: rdp-toolkit
Version: 9.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-yaml, openssh-client, freerdp2-x11
Maintainer: usekarne <usekarne@users.noreply.github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/usekarne/github-rdp-mega-toolkit
Description: Cross-platform RDP automation toolkit
 RDP Mega Toolkit provides automated RDP session management with
 multi-tunnel failover (serveo, localhost.run, cloudflare, localtunnel),
 built-in VM orchestration, multi-platform support (Kali/Windows/Android),
 and YAML-driven configuration. Includes bash completion and a doctor
 command for environment validation.
